{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 22,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] After that, Mussolini and Hitler got together through the Axis, and they didn't let any more Italian Jews go to universities.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With TWA, I had half a million miles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything first class for 35 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that I learned tremendous things going to different places, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And always you'll find-- you know, I was married for 24 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I-- we got divorced.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we talk today every day, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at that time, you know, I wanted from the camps, I wanted the freedom to do everything I want, you know, without too many restrictions.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't want children either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I think whatever I saw, you know, I was very shocked about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what I-- we got a daughter that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was part of my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I enjoyed-- my best way in life were from the late-- middle 40s to middle 80s.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when I really-- I grasped as much as I could from life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I made money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not too much, but I made a good living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And whatever-- you know, you don't know me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whatever I had, always I gave it away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I have nothing now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I live on Social Security.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what was it about?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About restrictions, death, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I want the freedom of me, to do anything I want, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I accomplished that, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, you know, I didn't realize I would be like this, not to work enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Part of it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Part of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a terrible time in life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I was lucky to go in the camps to the end of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Other people stayed many years.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
